Title: Fight Club
Plot: Mulder and Scully cross paths with two women who are identical and have followed each other across 17 states in the last three years, causing chaos and mayhem wherever they are.
GuestStars: Randall Tex Cobb, Art Evans, Jack McGee, Gene LeBell, Kathy Griffin, Arlene Pileggi, Steve Kiziak, Cory Blevins, John O'Brien, Christopher Michael, Brian Chenoweth, Jim Hanna, Nicole Bush, Paul Hansen Kim, John Mac
